The paper deals with lattices and their properties, which are commonly studied in the information theory (cs.IT) and computational complexity (cs.CC) sub-categories. The paper also discusses lattice-related problems, which are studied in the data structures (cs.DS) and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-categories.
